data.title: WARZONE Definition & Meaning
data.meta_description: Warzone definition: (during wartime) a combat area in which the rights of neutrals are suspended, as such an area on the high seas, where ships flying a neutral flag are subject to attack.. See examples of WARZONE used in a sentence.
